The first version of dpg4x was developed by me, Félix Medrano Sanz. But I am only
the last contributor in the history of the DPG format in Linux. This history
has evolved mainly over forums, with small contributions from a lot of great
linuxers.

I know I can't spread recognition as everyone deserves, please email me with 
corrections.


########################
### GBADEV.ORG FORUM ###
