############################
### EXQUISITE ICON THEME ###
############################

All the icons used by dpg4x, belong to the Exquisite icon theme. Included in 
kde-look under GPL license.

Thank you to Mimin Ladha (original Xp_Mad icon set), Ghast (action icons), 
Guppetto (KDE port) and Nick Bargnesi (build script).

http://kde-look.org/content/show.php?content=14788


###############
### PEXPECT ###
###############

dpg4x includes code from the pexpect library, by Noah Spurrier.

http://www.noah.org/wiki/Pexpect

The pexpect library is great and I use it often. I have included the code because
I just needed one function and I wanted to save on dependencies (there are too
many already).


